Package: synergize
Title: Easily analyze synergy data from the Janus drug printer. 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Emily", "Isenhart", , "emily.isenhart@roswellpark.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Easily analyze syergy data from the Janus drug printer. Includes 
    scripts to lazily read in absorbance files, process the protocol generated 
    by the drug printer, align the absorbance with the protocol, calculate 
    percent viability from absorbance data, and plot data using SynergyFinder. 
License: `use_mit_license()`, `use_gpl3_license()` or friends to pick a
    license
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
